Summary: I seen three moving stars and one half moon projected solid white light with a dark shade in it
divs: Sighting DetailsI was at a friends house sitting on the deck visiting while star gazing when from the west came a star shaped object heading straight East until it went out of sight.I then seen a star shaped object coming from the North heading straight South that crossed the path of the other star that passed to the East,It then changed direction for a short distance at flashing speed to the West then back East to it's flight path until out of sight. A star appeared heading North coming from the South which was in the same flight path of the south bound star,it then headed straight North over the Rice Lake airport.All objects had to be at least over 50 thousand feet in the sky. Then to the SE I seen a half moon shaped object flash solid white with a dark shade in it,the distance was hard to estimate but it looked like it was one half to a mile away,and about 300 feet high in the sky.
